00:35:01.030 --> 00:35:02.030
&gt;&gt;Junot Diaz: Yeah.

00:35:02.030 --> 00:35:03.030
&gt;&gt;male #3: To support art.

00:35:03.030 --> 00:35:05.260
&gt;&gt;Junot Diaz: No, I think it's a wonderful
