00:39:51.970 --> 00:39:58.290
military family, you have no idea what the
American military looks like at a global level.

00:39:58.290 --> 00:40:01.660
Those of us who are in military families,
we're like, we have a totally different sense

00:40:01.660 --> 00:40:03.160
of a map.

00:40:03.160 --> 00:40:05.220
Realistic fiction doesn't do a good job of
that.

00:40:05.220 --> 00:40:11.130
