a dictator, of one person with an immense

00:40:29.012 --> 00:40:34.650
amount of power, so while the future often,
not more than often, is predominantly white,

00:40:34.650 --> 00:40:39.870
a lot of the issues that people are wrestling
with are sort of the taboos that realistic

00:40:39.870 --> 00:40:42.410
literature doesn't like to address.

00:40:42.410 --> 00:40:47.740
So the one can recuperate even from the whitest
